{"tid":1126381,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"日本Fami通 「平成時代（1989-2019）最佳游戲」前三位公佈","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:49:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T16:29:01.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c0368967117a24d7397893dc609468e6c12563e3","tid":1126381,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:49:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rErMvhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrErMvhO.jpg&h=c7e1ac29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本Fami通雜志做了個「平成時代（1989-2019）最佳游戲」的調查，共有7100名以上玩家參與投票，前三位是：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>1. 超時空之鑰 Chrono Trigger（230票）</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrTZQhT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrTZQhT.jpg&h=11114474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《超時空之鑰》最早於1995年登陸 SFC 平台，玩家表示「游戲的故事、情節和音樂都是真正的傑作」、「就算時間流逝，和主角一起旅行的記憶無法忘卻」。本作得到了許多30多歲的玩家的熱愛，主要原因或許與阪口博信、鳥山明等參與了游戲制作的大人物有關，許多粉絲在投票的同時分享了大量有關本作的回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>2. 薩爾達傳說 曠野之息（209票）</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S687eKB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS687eKB.jpg&h=ba8de177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《塞爾達傳說 曠野之息》於2017年登陸 Switch 和 Wii U 平台，本作可以說是系列變革最大的一作，投票玩家表示「仿佛自己就生活在海拉爾」，無論年齡與性別，玩家都高度贊揚了游戲開放世界的充實內容。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3. 尼爾 自動人形（205票） ​​​​</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2YAdUKG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2YAdUKG.jpg&h=fa700c5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《尼爾 自動人形》最早於2017年登陸 PS4 與 PC 平台，投票玩家表示「從來沒有在任何游戲中體會到這份感動」、「游戲傳達了無法用文字表達的情感」，特別是很多20歲左右的年輕人對橫尾太郎塑造的獨特世界觀表示贊許。<br />\n<br />\n詳細的排名將在平成年最後一期《Fami通》中公布。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xFqJxwp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxFqJxwp.jpg&h=c7e421cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed05fb1286594282a9c6d4fa5bca199efd8d3353","tid":1126381,"uid":75050,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:11:13.000Z","msg":"得果七千幾人投，證明連Fami通都無乜人睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229331758e36e94d78640abd91aaa0cb2daf07cf","tid":1126381,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:19:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">全面進場</span>"},{"pid":"c62508dfa31389512972f3d438a697329c9300f4","tid":1126381,"uid":169133,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"頭三竟然無時之笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋以呢個年份來講 nier真係無理由上榜"},{"pid":"60436c3d36be82fd592ae8ffdcd1acf861fbb58c","tid":1126381,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62508dfa31389512972f3d438a697329c9300f4","tid":1126381,"uid":169133,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:23:40.000Z","msg":"頭三竟然無時之笛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋以呢個年份來講 nier真係無理由上榜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:26:09.000Z","msg":"年齡層面問題"},{"pid":"1f4ab2c1930b447b194528377c7238dbbce3a2ae","tid":1126381,"uid":38891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:28:00.000Z","msg":"metal gear呢？"},{"pid":"81844583a555acc2ac1b2b800acb573af1aba56d","tid":1126381,"uid":221419,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:31:19.000Z","msg":"二百幾票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚有代表性同公信力嘅投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b14f118640ba1070cf4498e8f1915a3b65940f4","tid":1126381,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1f4ab2c1930b447b194528377c7238dbbce3a2ae","tid":1126381,"uid":38891,"li